{"tid":374282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民族黨:【請加入聯署要求美國政府取消《香港關係法》】","createTime":"2017-08-25T15:29:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-28T06:50:50.000Z","uid":28366,"like":40,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0cbed7de74686f6904b2e58a58e5ffaaecda0e14","tid":374282,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T15:29:02.000Z","msg":"【請加入聯署要求美國政府取消《香港關係法》】<br />\n<br />\n敝黨日前向美國駐港領事館遞交請願信，要求美國取消《美國&mdash;香港政策法1992》 (即《香港關係法》)。請願信現開放網上聯署，歡迎各方人士參加。<br />\n<br />\n請願信內容請參考： <a href=\"https://goo.gl/8e83rX\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2F8e83rX&d=J7JE%2FUvgVmiymhQ0sLk4g0%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=b309d5ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/8e83rX</a><br />\n聯署連結：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/jcWzgY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FjcWzgY&d=J7JE%2FUvgVmiymhQ0sLk4g0%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=ffe2964d\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/jcWzgY</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://assets.change.org/photos/8/qs/zu/MQQsZuLaWmXlOhm-800x450-noPad.jpg?1503670034\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.change.org%2Fphotos%2F8%2Fqs%2Fzu%2FMQQsZuLaWmXlOhm-800x450-noPad.jpg%3F1503670034&h=af6f8869&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d94649071875493e10b55a637e2655ee15eb9942","tid":374282,"uid":131691,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T15:36:24.000Z","msg":"始終係民族黨玩得最盡<br />\n亂世下，睇嚟真係不落呢種重藥不可<br />\n加油呀，民族黨！"},{"pid":"4cff1344420d7ad15b52e1a2d3402c883d449bde","tid":374282,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T15:41:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8dd2847df8d5fb6157876d341efb382a97b4ccb","tid":374282,"uid":130247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T15:42:35.000Z","msg":"做法正確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5098c1d4c1bb39b4db6d7655421777bbb8998b7c","tid":